#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/blue_dragon_wyrmling.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Saving Throws** Dex +2, Con +4, Wis +2, Cha +4    \n"
"**Skills** Perception +4, Stealth +2    \n"
"**Damage Immunities** lightning    \n"
"**Senses** blindsight 10 ft., darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 14    \n"
"**Languages** Draconic    \n"
"**Challenge** 3 (700 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/blue_dragon_wyrmling.md:25
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Bite.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"8 (1d10 + 3) piercing damage plus 3 (1d6) lightning damage.    \n"
"**Lightning Breath (Recharge 5–6).** The dragon exhales lightning in a "
"30-­foot line that is 5 feet wide. Each creature in that line must make a DC "
"12 Dexterity saving throw, taking 22 (4d10) lightning damage on a failed "
"save, or half as much damage on a successful one.\n"
msgstr ""
